title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 14 2022
description:
Economist Steve Moore joins Clay and Buck to discuss Bidenflation, Democrats printing money and how the GOP needs to take a chainsaw to the budget and “cut, cut cut.” Tampa Bay head coach Todd Bowles didn’t get the woke memo on NFL racism, smacks down liberal reporters race-baiting questions. Ronna McDaniel, Chairwoman of the Republican Party, talks with C&B about GOP strategy for the midterms.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
